1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 16=

4
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,200
Qin Yu.

5
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,800
What are you doing?

6
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,800
Qin Yu.

7
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,400
What are you doing?

8
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,160
You've fallen for Xiaomi,

9
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,280
haven't you?

10
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,600
Don't forget why you came back.

11
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,880
Let me mark you.

12
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:54,440
That way, you'll be mine alone.

13
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,240
Don't paint in a draft anymore.

14
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,400
You'll catch a cold.

15
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,680
A promise is a promise.

16
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,480
If you can't keep it,

17
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,880
don't make it.

18
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,280
Wait for me to come back.

19
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:06,960
Xiaoduo.

20
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,000
Wait for me, alright?

21
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,360
You stole my identity.

22
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,880
You said you wanted to find the truth.

23
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,280
But look at yourself.

24
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,880
What are you doing now?

25
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,120
How can you do this to Xiaoduo?

26
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,640
What are you doing?

27
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,520
How can you do this to Xiaoduo?

28
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,160
It's okay now.

29
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,000
How can you face her?

30
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,680
It's okay.

31
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,920
It's okay.

32
00:02:29,930 --> 00:02:31,000
It's okay.

33
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,960
Qin Yu.

34
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,760
What are you doing?

35
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,560
Qin Yu.

36
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,800
What are you doing?

37
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,440
Qin Yu.

38
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,720
Qin Yu.

39
00:03:27,730 --> 00:03:28,480
Qin Yu.

40
00:03:28,490 --> 00:03:29,440
Qin Yu.

41
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,800
What are you doing?

42
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,920
Mr. Qin.

43
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,240
I heard you'll
be running the gallery now.

44
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,600
I'd like to apply for reinstatement.

45
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,600
I'm actually quite capable.

46
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,800
I've already received offers
from several partners.

47
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,560
I'll consider it.

48
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:26,000
Xiaomi just sent me a message.

49
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,280
She probably has something important
to ask me.

50
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,960
Your attitude, Mr. Qin,

51
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,280
will determine my answer.

52
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,120
Trust me.

53
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,200
Hiring me

54
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,560
will be worth every penny.

55
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:44,640
Xiaomi.

56
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,400
What did you want to see me about?

57
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,720
I just wanted to ask,

58
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,400
what were Qin Yu and Ye Xiaoduo
like together?

59
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,640
Looks like Mr. Qin

60
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,520
has really made you curious.

61
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,320
I just want to know
what their relationship was like.

62
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,600
To be honest,

63
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,920
I'm an outsider,
so I don't know much about it.

64
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,400
But there were rumors back then

65
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,280
that Ye Xiaoduo was trying
to steal your boyfriend.

66
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,320
But don't worry.

67
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,680
From what I can see,

68
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,960
Mr. Qin only has eyes for you.

69
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,520
Dr. Chen.

70
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,760
I think

71
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,760
I'm falling for someone I shouldn't.

72
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,080
Qin Yu told me before

73
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,440
that his name isn't really Qin Yu.

74
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,360
Then who is he?

75
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,880
He said his name is

76
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,560
Ji Ran.

77
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,960
Because of a twist of fate back then,

78
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,920
he borrowed Qin Yu's identity

79
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,080
and ended up being with me.

80
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,800
Does the name Ji Ran

81
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,600
ring any bells for you?

82
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,600
(That's impossible.)

83
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,200
(They may look the same,)

84
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,240
(but he and my brother)

85
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,800
(are completely different people.)

86
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,000
(Why would he pretend to be Ji Ran?)

87
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,400
Dr. Chen?

88
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:18,760
Dr. Chen?

89
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,240
Are you sure

90
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,480
you could love someone like that?

91
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,640
I don't want to keep searching
for the truth anymore.

92
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,480
And I don't want
to recover my memories anymore.

93
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,560
I love him.

94
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,680
No matter who he is, I love him.

95
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,320
Xiaomi.

96
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,960
A life without memories is incomplete.

97
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,840
Are you really willing

98
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,720
to accept an incomplete life?

99
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,240
Even though

100
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,120
I don't have a past,

101
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,840
I know I still have a future.

102
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,480
Thank you for everything
during this time, Dr. Chen.

103
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,640
You don't need to try
to persuade me anymore.

104
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,720
What right do you have
to talk about the future?

105
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,040
Today,

106
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,040
did you go to see Qiao Xiaomi

107
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,000
and try to drive a wedge between them?

108
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,440
Idiot!

109
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,160
Listen carefully.

110
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,880
Don't do anything reckless.

111
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,400
If you dare ruin my plans,

112
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:44,040
you'll pay dearly for it.

113
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,840
Right now,

114
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,480
not only can we not break them up,

115
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:56,400
we need to make them
fall hopelessly in love.

116
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,600
(I've searched for so long.)

117
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,840
(I've been piecing it all together
for so long.)

118
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,640
(And it turns out what
I've been searching for all along)

119
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,240
(was my own heart.)

120
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,800
Qin Yu.

121
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,880
No matter who you are,

122
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,440
I accept it.

123
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:25,360
(All this pain,)

124
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,960
(these blurry shadows,)

125
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,120
(these fragments I can never grasp,)

126
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,760
(goodbye.)

127
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,280
It's no fun
blowing off steam by yourself.

128
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,440
Want me

129
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,400
to blow off some steam with you?

130
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,160
I'd rather not.

131
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,760
Then what do you want to do?

132
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:42,600
I want a drink.

133
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,000
Let's go.

134
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,200
I'm sorry.

135
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,440
I'm sorry.

136
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,120
I'm sorry.

137
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:19,080
It's okay.

138
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,760
I forgive you.

139
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,000
Just be nicer to me from now on.

140
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:32,920
You goof.

141
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,120
I'm sorry.

142
00:11:09,650 --> 00:11:11,720
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

143
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:15,140
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

144
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:18,630
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

145
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:22,620
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

146
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,720
♪Let me go, set me free♪

147
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:29,760
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

148
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:35,710
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

149
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:39,200
♪The freedom you gave me♪

150
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:42,840
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

151
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:46,370
♪Love can barely move forward♪

152
00:11:46,370 --> 00:11:50,150
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

153
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:53,490
♪The closeness I long for♪

154
00:11:53,490 --> 00:11:57,880
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

155
00:11:58,290 --> 00:12:00,110
♪I don't want to break free♪

156
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:05,480
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
